# Automations runtime: SDK + runner are installed by the daemon at startup
# from embedded assets. User scripts under `automations/` should be checked
# in case-by-case (not auto-ignored).
/automations/.runtime/
/automations/node_modules/
/automations/package.json
# The SDK source bundled into the daemon binary lives under a node_modules/
# layout so the runner can `import "@symphony/automation"` directly. Keep it
# tracked despite the global node_modules/ ignore above.
!crates/meridian-automations/runtime-assets/node_modules/
